Questions from Death Note
by meganliu » Thu 12.31.2009 3:36 am I'm sorry I keep posting cause I really have toooo.. many questions and I'm eager to figure them out.Here are some questions I met when I was reading Death Note, the manga.二人の選ばれし者の壮絶な戦いが始まる。死因を書かなければ、全くが心臓麻痺となる。　I copied the above sentences from the manga, but I can't understand parts of them. Firstly, 選ばれし. The しhere is quite confusing. What's its usage here? Or should it be 選ばれる者?Second one is the となる. If I'm right, the grammar is 名詞/形動+になる. So why と here?
meganliu
