Re: Questions from Death Note
by keatonatron » Thu 12.31.2009 5:46 am From WWJDICT:選ばれし者 【えらばれしもの】 (n) the chosen one; the chosen ones; the select fewFeel free to slap your forehead at any time となる is simply a more formal/stiff form of になる. The meaning is exactly the same.
Searching for models and actors in Tokyo. No experience required!
